The open plaza is finally done. Glad the area opens up. Refreshed ceiling and flooring on Level 1. Basement 1 still under renovation. Lib still under renovation.

Previous review:
A neighbourhood mall in bukit batok. Currently under revamp so some parts of it are hoarded up. The lib is also closes due to the renovation. Interior of mall generally not affected. Didn't like the bulky push carts blocking the corridor. It makes the walking unpleasant as the corridor is narrow.

Good neighbour tenant mix with food, clothing and grocery options.", 'languageCode': 'en'}
